Boyfriend?

56
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:23,040
Not really. Never stayed
in one place long enough.

57
00:04:41,999 --> 00:04:44,879
It's a bit basic.

58
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:46,720
Not when you've slept in barracks.

59
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:58,560
I was going to close a deal
on a shop in Dublin tomorrow.

60
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:01,519
What do you trade in?

61
