Thank you. I made it myself.

72
00:05:43,639 --> 00:05:45,760
Where are you from? Bristol.

73
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:50,760
What were you going to Dublin for?
Auntie Nora's ill and Uncle Finn
can't manage the children.

74
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:55,400
