with the currency and
money management. David Ward.

85
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,239
Sally-Anne Hope.

86
00:07:02,239 --> 00:07:05,999
Deborah Morrison, and it's
spelt how Deborah Kerr spells it.

87
00:07:05,999 --> 00:07:09,400
Your background stories
should incorporate your skills.

88
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:11,759
