which emit radio waves
and then look for reflections...

101
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:04,320
Bananas! Of course,
bananas are far more interesting.

102
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,480
Look at all this!

103
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,880
We'd just come off rationing in '53.

104
