145
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:45,519
Of course, when it was over,
we were supposed to revert to
being dutiful wives and daughters.

146
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:48,999
But I'd got the taste for it. No
pig-headed man tells me what to do.

147
00:11:48,999 --> 00:11:50,839
Ah.

148
00:11:50,839 --> 00:11:53,760
"Sky Gipsy"?

149
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:56,399
After the engine.

150
00:11:56,399 --> 00:12:00,999
The de Havilland Gipsy Six -
a work of genius.

151
00:12:00,999 --> 00:12:05,359
Tuned with a higher compression
ratio to squeeze more energy
from its fuel mixture.

152
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,559
Can I take her up?

153
