to come and watch.

166
00:12:50,959 --> 00:12:52,600
Ever the business man, eh, John?

167
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:59,759
That's an American accent, isn't it?

168
00:12:59,759 --> 00:13:02,200
That's right.

169
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,639
So how did you end up here,

170
00:13:04,639 --> 00:13:07,400
