186
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:18,520
My parents are dead,
so I came down here to start afresh.

187
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:21,079
So they didn't leave you
a house or anything?

188
00:14:22,639 --> 00:14:24,120
No.

189
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:29,119
