You expect equality AND chivalry?

202
00:15:37,399 --> 00:15:42,079
I don't see why they should be
mutually exclusive.
Well, if it makes you happy.

203
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:50,159
Your chair, ma'am.

204
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,920
